            <div class="fc-4c">
                <h5 class="aboutus">About Us</h5>
                <p>At the Wellcome Genome Campus we undertake genome and biodata research. We provide bioinformatics services to the world and we deliver vital training in genomics and biodata to scientists and clinicians. We are at the interface of research and industry translating science into tangible societal benefits.</p>
